<hr>

Now for bottom-margin settings.

These can be applied to any and all sections, duet or single.

<h1>DEFAULT SETTING</h1>

\\11
"Default" setting (two line-heights tall)
\\22
Demonstration.
\\11
Hello
\\22
World.

\\s
______________________________

<h1>JOIN SETTING</h1>

\\11j
"Join" setting (one line-height tall)
\\22j
Demonstration.
\\11j
Hello
\\22j
World.

\\s
______________________________

<h1>QUICK SETTING</h1>

\\11q
"Quick" setting (no bottom margin at all)
\\22q
Demonstration
\\11q
Hello
\\22q
World.